text:
if you want to find your biggest tweets, search:

from:yourhandle min_retweets:1000

apparently my biggest were calling out engineering elitism, calling out google’s corporate greed, calling out twitter’s HR inhumanity aaaaand… pokemon.

if it's helpful I always math it out as:

2^(log2(number_of_valid_characters ^ number_characters) - log2(num_invites)) * 15ms / num_sessions_machine / num_machines

so, 36 options, 7 characters long, 65000 invites, 8 sessions, 1000 AWS instances --> every 2.2s
